		<link rel="enclosure" type="image" href="https://olifer.org/" />
		<updated>2020-11-30T00:00:00Z</updated>
		<content>&lt;p&gt;Since the release of macOS Sierra, when in Finder, it is now possible to use the shortcut: &lt;kbd&gt;CMD&lt;/kbd&gt; + &lt;kbd&gt;SHIFT&lt;/kbd&gt; + &lt;kbd&gt;.&lt;/kbd&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
